<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Farewell Invitation</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body{
    background:#111;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
    font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
}

.invitation{
    width:500px;
    padding:40px;
    border:3px solid #caa74a;
    text-align:center;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0b0b0b,#1a1a1a);
    color:#e6c56a;
    box-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(202,167,74,0.3);
}

.small{
    font-size:14px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
}

.title{
    font-size:70px;
    font-family:'Great Vibes', cursive;
    margin:10px 0;
}

.subtitle{
    font-size:26px;
    font-family:'Great Vibes', cursive;
}

.description{
    margin:25px 0;
    font-size:16px;
    line-height:1.5;
}

.line{
    border-top:1px solid #caa74a;
    width:60%;
    margin:20px auto;
}

.date{
    font-size:20px;
    font-weight:600;
}

.place{
    font-size:22px;
    margin-top:10px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="invitation">

<div class="small">YOU ARE INVITED TO</div>

<div class="subtitle">Our</div>

<div class="title">Farewell</div>

<div class="subtitle">Party</div>

<div class="description">
Let's celebrate the wonderful memories, laughter, and achievements 
before you move on to a new chapter.
</div>

<div class="line"></div>

<div class="date">
Monday, March 30 2026 <br>
AT 2:00 PM
</div>

<div class="place">Sangford School</div>

<div class="line"></div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
